<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= lang %>">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>QR Menu &mdash; Renome</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,500&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: #f8f7f4;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .qr-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 48px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 380px;
      width: 100%;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      border: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .qr-card__logo {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      margin: 0 auto 16px;
      display: block;
    }

    .qr-card__name {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .qr-card__subtitle {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #888;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .qr-card__code {
      background: #fff;
      border: 2px solid #2d5a27;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 16px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .qr-card__code img {
      display: block;
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
    }

    .qr-card__cta {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .qr-card__cta-line {
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .qr-card__cta-line--secondary {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #666;
    }

    .qr-card__desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #999;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .qr-card__desc + .qr-card__desc {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .qr-card__lang-divider {
      width: 20px;
      height: 1px;
      background: #ddd;
      margin: 10px auto;
    }

    .qr-card__divider {
      width: 40px;
      height: 2px;
      background: #2d5a27;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .qr-card__address {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #aaa;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .qr-card__wifi {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding-top: 16px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
    }

    .qr-card__wifi strong {
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .qr-print {
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .qr-print__btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 32px;
      background: #2d5a27;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .qr-print__btn:hover {
      background: #1e3d1a;
    }

    @media print {
      body {
        background: #fff;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .qr-card {
        box-shadow: none;
        border: none;
        padding: 32px 24px;
        max-width: 100%;
      }
      .qr-print {
        display: none;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 420px) {
      .qr-card {
        padding: 32px 24px;
        border-radius: 16px;
      }
      .qr-card__name {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .qr-card__code img {
        width: 180px;
        height: 180px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="qr-card">
    <img src="/img/logo-clean.png" alt="Renome" class="qr-card__logo">
    <div class="qr-card__name">Renome</div>
    <div class="qr-card__subtitle">Italian Café / Итальянское Кафе</div>

    <div class="qr-card__code">
      <img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=440x440&data=https://renome.zeabur.app&color=2d5a27&bgcolor=ffffff" alt="QR Code">
    </div>

    <div class="qr-card__cta">
      <div class="qr-card__cta-line">Scanează meniul</div>
      <div class="qr-card__cta-line qr-card__cta-line--secondary">Сканируй меню</div>
    </div>
    <div class="qr-card__desc">
      Deschide camera telefonului și scanează codul QR<br>
      pentru a vedea meniul și a comanda online
    </div>
    <div class="qr-card__lang-divider"></div>
    <div class="qr-card__desc">
      Открой камеру телефона и отсканируй QR-код,<br>
      чтобы посмотреть меню и заказать онлайн
    </div>

    <div class="qr-card__divider"></div>
    <div class="qr-card__address">
      str. Calea Ieșilor 57, Bălți / ул. Каля Ешилор 57, Бэлць<br>
      Zilnic / Ежедневно: 10:00 — 01:00
    </div>

    <div class="qr-print">
      <button class="qr-print__btn" onclick="window.print()">Printează / Распечатать</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
